      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and definitely has plenty of adventures left in it! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so it runs smoothly and still looks fantastic pulling into the driveway. It has a tiny bit of 'character' here and there from normal use, but it's been super reliable for me. If you're looking for a dependable, great-looking car that's ready to hit the road today, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
